IMHO the change log of the assignee field (IssueImpl based) and the {{UserCFType}} custom field should not be different. 

Example *Assignee*
{code}
Bearbeiter	 Helmer Johanna [ p099191 ]	 Maehlfrau Lara [ p083555 ]
{code}

Example *UserCFType*
{code}
Entwickler	 p099191	 p083555
{code}

In our projects the technical user ids provided by ldap system are little bit strange. So it's not easy for a user without in deep JIRA skill to identify the previous _Entwickler_.

The reason for the missing _real name_ part is that the getChangelogString method of {{UserCFType}} returns {{null}}.

Could you fix that?

